<div type="definition">

    <p resp="#CH" modified="2020-11-06T21:43:06.103+09:00">MALE ADULT who is NOT MARRIED. </p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. There are no competing terms for "bachelor" in classical Chinese. The current word is kuàng fū 曠夫 (opp. yuàn nu# 怨女 "unmarried woman of marrigeable age").</p>
